OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAn overcast start with periods
OL,6,Fof rain, heavy at times, combining
OL,7,Fwith gales to bring decidedly un-
OL,8,FSpring like weather. Clearing to
OL,9,Fblustery showers in Argyll late
OL,10,Fmorning, and elsewhere for the
OL,11,Fafternoon, as showers turn wintry
OL,12,Facross higher ground.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FBlustery showers pushing
OL,15,Facross the area on strong west to
OL,16,Fsouthwest winds. Outbreaks frequent
OL,17,Fand heavy in Argyll, occasional
OL,18,Felsewhere and turning wintry to quite
OL,19,Flow levels.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,179,160,301,260,100,100
