OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FShowers continuing, frequent
OL,6,Fin west, occasional in east. Outbreaks
OL,7,Flighter than Thursday night with sleet
OL,8,Fand snow becoming confined to the
OL,9,Fhills of Argyll. Limited brighter
OL,10,Fspells best in east.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,13,Ffor Saturday focused in west. Rain
OL,14,Fearly Sunday, clearing to blustery
OL,15,Fshowers by afternoon, these wintry
OL,16,Facross hills. Scattered showers then
OL,17,Fperiods of rain for Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
